  "_merge_instructions": "Merge: copy agent{} into opencode.json or opencode.jsonc. Keep your mcp and permission blocks. Set default_agent to flowforge if desired. Models use opencode-go/* — configure that provider and API keys in OpenCode. Do not use placeholder file-reference syntax with ellipsis inside JSON strings (OpenCode treats every file: reference as a real path)."
